{"tid":677479,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再次呼籲，咪撚入浸大","createTime":"2018-05-25T08:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T08:38:13.000Z","uid":56902,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd034d16f260fd1c3d43034f8648d43616b0f82","tid":677479,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/527715/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%97%E5%93%B2%E7%B3%BB%E5%85%A8%E8%81%B7%E8%AC%9B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E7%BA%8C%E7%B4%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F527715%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%2593%25B2%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25B4%2584&d=YbuBPTZzxgtB6n4KcdqCxx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=1e1d578a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F527715%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%2593%25B2%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25B4%2584&h=b6093ed6\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/527715/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%97%E5%93%B2%E7%B3%BB%E5%85%A8%E8%81%B7%E8%AC%9B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E7%BA%8C%E7%B4%84</a><br />\n<br />\n浸大宗哲系全職講師全部不獲續約<br />\n更新：2018/05/25 16:07<br />\n浸會大學宗教及哲學系的全職講師下一學年全部不獲續約，校方提出可改為兼職時薪制，月入減少近半，但課時反而增加，有校董批評浸大刻薄，要求校方讓全職講師留任。<br />\n<br />\n浸大宗哲系現在只有三名全職講師，其中高級講師即將退休，餘下兩人、年資都有六年以上。浸大校董王凱峰指，校方早前以教學量減少為由，今年九月不再與兩位講師續約，但上個月又提出以時薪一千元，請回他們做兼職。<br />\n<br />\n月入由原本約四萬七元，減至二萬六千多元，沒有福利，但教的學分反而多了，原本每星期上課九小時，改做兼職，下學期要教十四小時。王凱峰問過首席副校長，對方這樣回覆，「所有事都合法」。<br />\n<br />\n王凱峰批評校方只是重視研究，不重視教學，要求校長錢大康及校董會主席鄭恩基繼續聘用這批全職講師。講師轉為兼職後，會沒有自己的辦公室，暑假期間亦用不到大學圖書館。<br />\n<br />\n浸大回應指，是按照既定程序和守則招聘教學人員，又指部分院系早前因為三三四新學制，聘請多了合約員工，因應學生人數回落要調整。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入浸大又要讀蝗語，又要擔心被人滅系，又要曬時間讀d無謂嘅通識科。<br />\n唔好入嚟讀呀！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a0c04b1e5fc7338d33d246f88a8b4f2b6bef0f1","tid":677479,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/163803_1e974a9c12c1274a84591e7f412047de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F163803_1e974a9c12c1274a84591e7f412047de.png&h=24653c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}